<p>Finally, you can use text search to do zero-shot classification.  Try adding â€œPersonâ€, â€œPlaceâ€, and â€œThingâ€ to your text gallery.  Then search for the text â€œVeniceâ€, and get â€œPlaceâ€ as the top result.  Search with an image of a toaster, and get â€œThingâ€ as the top guess.</p>

